description:
A chance to redefine living excellence is yours for the taking with an opportunity rarely found in a thriving upcoming suburb, Wynnum West! From the kerb to the rear boundary, this is your chance to live a life of your own design, in a premier location less than 25 minutes from the Brisbane CBD!

- Established dwelling ready to be renovated or removed for your dream homes
- Development Approval obtained for a 2 Lot Subdivision
- Two approved 404m2 lots
- Premier road offering public transport connectivity, access to highly regarded private and public schools
- Stone throw to dining and bayside parkland mecca

This is an exciting and rare opportunity for the astute developer wanting to take advantage of a site that's had all the town planning work done for you. Providing an easy-build blank canvas on both lots, there is development approval already obtained for two 404m2 lots along with removal of the existing house.

A prime opportunity to experience that brand new custom feel, the location is second to none with superb accessibility to the vibrant inner-Brisbane sanctum! Better that you can walk to multiple lifestyle hubs and park precincts whilst you won't compromise on every day convenience with a raft of amenities at your door; multiple schooling options, shopping and both public and road transport corridors.

Set to be auctioned on-site on mid January, don't miss your chance to grab a rare build opportunity in a coveted Bayside location! For further information please contact Dominic Kinnane or Sara Curley
